OOC:This is a time warp then to take care of the slight problem that we had earlier right?
Cooley:
Looks to KitKat confused. "I might not be the one that you are talking about. I am just normal Cooley," He smiles to her, "And besides I have never had someone Bow to me before so Don't bow to me please. and fill me in on this whole lord bit," He says with a smile. 

shadowess_azogoth <shadowess_azogoth@...> wrote:
KitKat::

She sat down and looked up at Cooley. "So, my lord, when will we 
engage in your brilliant plans?" she said with a smile. So far, she 
still had her Matrix holders intact. She had given one to Cooley, but 
the other two she knew of were still connected to her spark. Hence 
her thoughts that the Matrix hated her.
